            <div class=3D"field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summ=
ary field--label-hidden field--item"><p>An EIN is a federal tax ID number f=
or businesses, tax-exempt organizations and other entities.</p>

<p>You can get an EIN for free directly from the IRS in minutes.&nbsp;<a ar=
ia-label=3D"Link Apply online" data-entity-substitution=3D"canonical" data-=
