<div class=3D"collapsible-item-heading panel-heading" id=3D"headingCollapsi=
ble1747238390991" role=3D"tab">
<h4 class=3D"collapsible-item-title panel-title" id=3D"lostormisplaced"><a =
aria-controls=3D"collapseCollapsible1747238390991" aria-expanded=3D"false" =
class=3D"collapsed collapsible-item-title-link pup-accordion-chevron-rt" da=
ta-toggle=3D"collapse" href=3D"https://www.irs.gov/businesses/employer-iden=
tification-number#collapseCollapsible1747238390991" role=3D"button" data-on=
ce=3D"links-once">Lost or forgot EIN</a></h4>
</div>

<div aria-labelledby=3D"accordion_header_help" class=3D"collapse collapsibl=
e-item-collapse panel-collapse" id=3D"collapseCollapsible1747238390991" rol=
e=3D"tabpanel">
<div class=3D"table-responsive">
<div class=3D"collapsible-item-body panel-body"><p class=3D"visually-hidden=
">&nbsp;</p>
<p><a id=3D"lost" name=3D"lost"></a>To find a missing EIN, try these steps:=
</p>

<ul>
	<li>Look for it on the notice we issued when you applied for an EIN</li>
	<li>Contact the bank that has your business account</li>
	<li>Check with agencies where you=E2=80=99ve applied for state or local li=
censes</li>
	<li>Look on past business tax returns</li>
</ul>

<p>If you still can=E2=80=99t find it, call us at <a href=3D"tel:800-829-49=
33">800-829-4933</a> Monday to Friday 7 a.m. - 7p.m. ET. We=E2=80=99ll veri=
fy your identity and provide the number over the phone if you=E2=80=99re au=
thorized to receive it.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class=3D"collapsible-item panel panel-default" data-fix-id=3D"Collapsi=
